The paper focuses on improving the efficiency of distributed deep learning on GPU clusters, which involves both distributed computing (cs.DC) and machine learning (cs.LG). The specific application of deep learning is in image classification (cs.CV), and the paper discusses the optimization of communication between layers (cs.NE) and the use of a hybrid communication scheme (cs.SY).
